    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated inline-six engineering. The S54B32 engine delivers linear power through six individual throttle bodies, with the critical rod bearing service and VANOS solenoid updates already completed. The drivetrain features a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual mated to a functional M-Variable limited-slip differential. Chassis integrity is verified with a reinforced subframe and factory-spec bushings. Every mechanical component, from the dual-mass flywheel to the cross-drilled rotors, is in peak operational state. This is a pristine, documentation-heavy example for those who value mechanical transparency and OEM+ standards.",
