      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a factory-fresh finish that must be seen to be believed. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections, and has been protected by a premium ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the leather seats show absolutely zero bolster wear, the dashboard is pristine with no UV damage, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented full-service history with every scheduled maintenance interval performed by factory-trained technicians. The drive is tight, responsive, and completely silent. It has never seen rain or snow, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to own what is arguably the finest example of this model currently available.",
      "price": 46500.0,
